Summary: It looked like a double decker bus,with double sets of blackened windows and just as big,which is why we noticed it so easily
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Elkhart Lake
There were no other sightings in Elkhart Lake on or around May 31st 2004
divs: Sighting DetailsWE were driving home from St Ann Wi. when we saw this huge-round shaped object flying low and extremely slow,making no noise approaching us, It looked to me like a double decker bus, I counted about 6-windows on it. It stopped, and some small little lighted spheres started to surround it then they scattered into different directions,I tried to focus on just a few,so as to remember what I was seeing, then it continued,again moving very slowly. Since this isnt the first time I witnessed something I trained myself to remain calm and remember what I am looking at. I just cant stop talking about it,or get it off my mind ! The spheres took off and disappeared, but the bus,I described it,kept moving slowly along.
